Outcome: Ratings for interest in single life. Predictors: Political Orientation & Age. Random intercept and random slope for country.

Political, ethnic and religious similarity

H2a Preference for similarity in political beliefs

H2a There is no linear link between right-wing political orientation and womens preferences for partners similar political beliefs and values when controlling for a quadratic link. There is a positive quadratic link between right-wing political orientation and womens preferences for partners similar political beliefs and values when controlling for a linear link. Outcome: Preference ratings for partners similar political beliefs and values. Predictors: Political Orientation & Age. Random intercept and random slope for country.

Models
model_pref_politicalsim_robustcheck = lmer(pref_politicalsim ~ political_orientation + I(political_orientation^2) + age +
                                 (1+political_orientation|country),
